1.25
log
@Revised the source code proprietary statement.
@
text
@//==============================================================================
// IBM Confidential
//
// OCO Source Materials
//
// Watson Implosion Technology
//
// (C) Copyright IBM Corp. 1993, 2011  All Rights Reserved
